<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF3A6A85FD2190031AF9B334" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF3A6A85FD2190031DE1BD91" blockId="193.[728,1327,1626,2054]" pageId="193" pageNumber="955">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF3A6A85FD2190031D79BD49" bold="true" box="[733,889,1626,1659]" pageId="193" pageNumber="955">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FC7B90031B27BD49" authority="Boie, 1825" authorityName="Boie" authorityYear="1825" box="[903,1319,1626,1659]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dasycneme">Vespertilio dasycneme Boie, 1825</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="74FC3CA3FF3A6A85FD2490DF1DE1BD91" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3783319779" box="[728,993,1670,1699]" pageId="193" pageNumber="955">
Jutland, 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF3A6A85FCAA90DF1DDDBD91" box="[854,989,1670,1699]" name="Denmark" pageId="193" pageNumber="955">Denmark</collectingCountry>
.
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF3A6A85FD2290F01AF9B334" blockId="193.[728,1327,1626,2054]" pageId="193" pageNumber="955">
Subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FC8290F01DD3BDF8" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[894,979,1705,1738]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
; sole member of the 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FD1C90881D62BDC0" authorityName="Boie" authorityYear="1825" box="[736,866,1745,1778]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dasycneme">dasycneme</taxonomicName>
species group. The relationship of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FCA890A11A0CBC2B" authorityName="Boie" authorityYear="1825" box="[852,1036,1784,1817]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dasycneme">M. dasycneme</taxonomicName>
to other species in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FC5F91791DF7BC73" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[931,1015,1824,1857]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
is relatively uncertain and there do not appear to be any species closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FC2E91361A85BCA2" authorityName="Boie" authorityYear="1825" box="[978,1157,1903,1936]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dasycneme">M. dasycneme</taxonomicName>
, supporting the recognition of its monospecific species group. The forms 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FC0691E71A43BCED" authorityName="J. E. Gray" authorityYear="1844" box="[1018,1091,1982,2015]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">major</taxonomicName>
and lmnophilus are synonyms of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF3A6A85FC3691BC1A4DB334" authorityName="Boie" authorityYear="1825" box="[970,1101,2021,2054]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dasycneme">dasycneme</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF3A6A85FF849E481F3FB349" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FF3A6A85FF849E481F3FB349" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398857" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398857" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398857/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="193" pageNumber="955" targetBox="[118,710,1637,2052]" targetPageId="193">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF3A6A85FF849E481F3FB349" blockId="193.[116,1325,2065,3474]" pageId="193" pageNumber="955">
